Talented Kizz Daniel has been ecstatic since his incredibly mesmerising visuals of the smash-hit track ‘Buga’ featuring Tekno Miles hit over two million views plus on YouTube in just 24 hours. The singer took to his Instagram story to share his achievement. The massive hit has seen Heads of Governments in Africa and beyond jump on the dance challenge   Wizkid, Simi lead NET Honours Class of 2022 nominees     Actor Chidi Mokeme mourns sister, cousin     Stop spreading fake news about me – Portable   The video adds grooving to this infectious new anthem is further celebrated in a cascade of vivacious colors that do justice to the monster hit. It is directed by TG Omori and shot on locations in Lagos and Abuja.